Requirements
X7CLOUD  requires php 5 or higher and has been tested up to php 5
The webservice is compatible with apache/iis and above and in some cases requires some additional plug ins to work properly.

New install: this is the first time you install x7 in your server

   1. Download the framework zip file
   2. Extract the contents of the zip file to your local hard drive
   3. Open to the basic_example.php script.
   4. Config the script as you wish.
   5. Go to your webbrowser, open the script and add the Get query parameters basic_example.php?1111=0&0000=0 , press enter then you will see all example modules. 
   6. Click en any module

